            <div><span style="font-size: 14px; text-align: inherit; background-color: transparent;">We wanted to know, so we decided to find out â€” and here's the second report from our developer compensation data series.</span></div>

<div>&nbsp;</div>

<div>It turns out that 65.8% of global remote devs included in our report receive devices, and over half (57%) have flexible working hours. An emerging benefit reported by those in Spanish-speaking countries? English classes.</div>

<div>&nbsp;</div>

<div><span style="font-size: 14px; text-align: inherit; background-color: transparent;"><a href="https://arc.dev/employer-blog/remote-developer-benefits-study-2022/?utm_source=sendgrid&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=arc-newsletter&amp;utm_content=20220419">Check out the full report here</a>&nbsp;ðŸ‘€</span></div>
