<div>&nbsp;</div>

<div><em>"Zooming out to look at both review sentiment and frequency of mentions, it's clear that remote work has become a major â€” and negative â€” part of interns' experience."</em></div>

<div>&nbsp;</div>

<div>If you're offering remote internships, you'll need to be deliberate in figuring out how to mentor online, as these interns have reported communication and connection struggles.</div>
